"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[feature] Integrated LLM Provider Configuration: The user expressed frustration with the previous approach and emphasized the need for a unified installation script that configures all LLM providers. This update reflects the implementation of that requirement, allowing the tool to dynamically identify and configure available models using API keys and OAuth for authentication. This centralizes the setup process and enables integration with a wider range of LLM services.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"wgr2uz","at":1782088664240},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09975388,-0.03676523,0.05471404,-0.09212118,-0.03944875,0.00135627,-0.03363936,-0.01472564,0.02340557,-0.07491713,0.01845894,-0.02007856,0.05936765,0.00747477,0.03698412,0.0139744,-0.00984257,0.01937461,0.00038206,0.07904881,0.09531343,-0.00564222,0.04661905,-0.00070397,-0.04780565,0.04086103,-0.03979017,-0.02089782,-0.04683151,-0.21351594,0.04269299,-0.01120494,0.04562424,-0.03224297,-0.02521682,-0.03255799,-0.07315086,0.02783046,-0.01554171,0.05363806,0.00931312,-0.04231035,-0.04356924,-0.04484059,-0.02553087,-0.0919323,-0.02861369,-0.02650488,-0.02682462,-0.0062679,0.04457366,0.00325778,0.00559952,0.04841151,0.00020091,0.04450874,-0.00332521,0.02453096,0.03506821,0.07410014,0.05135743,0.04670154,-0.2097867,0.10784735,0.01992829,0.03892775,-0.01413328,0.00343917,0.07839307,0.05719408,-0.0724657,-0.04192466,0.01199621,-0.00374927,0.05130525,0.02202214,0.01176341,0.00970569,0.03352649,-0.04255247,0.00019112,0.05024519,-0.00664032,-0.07875501,-0.02991403,-0.03003363,-0.01467842,-0.03838798,-0.02817771,0.04135614,-0.02980116,-0.00149021,-0.05833353,0.03410173,-0.01062966,0.01101444,0.02333188,-0.0257014,-0.10050821,0.13845815,-0.02875546,0.01446653,-0.01427887,-0.02560263,0.03790442,-0.02542784,-0.02859267,-0.01222777,-0.02438417,-0.00194623,-0.02847665,0.02143232,0.06471416,-0.0616478,-0.011315