"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[discovery] Hermes Model Discovery and Credential Management: The user is performing reverse engineering on the Hermes system to understand its model discovery mechanisms, credential management, and authentication methods (OAuth/API Keys). This investigation aims to replicate Hermes's sophisticated setup experience within the Hive-Mind tool, specifically by integrating model selection into the `install.sh` script and supporting a wide array of providers like LM Studio, Ollama Cloud, and NVIDIA.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"10wus2l","at":1782088664270},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06321176,0.02074512,0.03434565,-0.08808172,-0.02122417,0.0369769,0.02409321,0.02200561,0.00559973,0.00715193,0.05416403,-0.05627568,-0.02018364,0.02866587,0.04712464,-0.03748111,0.00837834,0.02025574,0.03245467,0.04189794,0.03593579,-0.02745924,0.00850384,-0.02792375,-0.03315393,0.03005348,-0.02421371,-0.03403236,-0.0266703,-0.23611902,0.01897187,-0.03820801,0.02335331,-0.00222074,0.00771846,-0.0342558,-0.05644792,-0.00353093,-0.02598408,0.01737065,-0.00172264,-0.01558678,0.0259114,-0.01951097,-0.00101255,-0.04167743,-0.00876156,0.0050934,-0.04642016,-0.07025317,0.00748747,0.0196963,-0.00929903,0.00593267,0.04660329,0.0342553,0.05050015,0.0234812,0.0129234,0.06268338,0.00607723,0.02304181,-0.21992026,0.08094063,0.06875467,0.05285291,-0.04062636,-0.02955194,0.01717135,0.0131264,-0.03894603,-0.00615041,-0.00808518,0.0153845,0.06129171,0.03121598,-0.03143519,-0.05025747,-0.00574724,-0.03917683,-0.01190234,0.02108626,-0.01142946,-0.0414465,0.02317975,-0.02771722,0.01021519,-0.00148232,0.00796605,-0.03885463,-0.05473338,-0.00869617,-0.01181651,0.02327975,-0.00171245,0.00641479,0.03435999,0.02991737,-0.0482886,0.13256404,-0.00514107,0.00970108,-0.05228469,-0.09175666,0.0588195,-0.04171026,-0.01806289,-0.07249411,0.03356782,0.02333545,-0.00000681,-0.00153692,0.07441359,-0.0