"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[discovery] Hermes Configuration Details: Analysis of the `/home/michel/.hermes/config.yaml` file provides a comprehensive view of Hermes's operational configuration. It highlights the primary LLM provider (`lmstudio`) and a prioritized list of fallback providers, along with strategies for managing credentials. The detailed agent settings, including personality configurations and various timeouts, reveal Hermes's sophisticated interaction model. Furthermore, the configuration for terminal, web, and auxiliary services, along with display and custom provider settings, offers insights into how Hermes integrates and manages different functionalities and LLM services. This information is crucial for replicating a similar level of integration and user experience in Hive-Mind.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"13dmd9i","at":1782088664447},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04822515,-0.00678705,0.04063784,-0.08641282,0.0227666,-0.01334428,-0.01592141,0.02457883,0.00697583,-0.08174975,0.01212786,-0.03368993,0.04322566,0.03267261,0.03518128,0.0034798,0.03625835,0.00273125,0.02317587,0.06600348,0.05714558,-0.03140721,0.03440792,-0.03224691,-0.0391381,0.03294646,-0.00735581,-0.03702661,-0.03407245,-0.2119936,0.05662605,-0.02305686,-0.00122078,-0.00641014,-0.00906639,-0.00857173,-0.05320511,-0.012541,-0.02421012,0.00698052,0.01519398,-0.03030129,-0.00301619,-0.00362863,-0.02813707,-0.07314885,0.01950725,-0.02087921,-0.05284283,-0.04324092,0.01022685,-0.00123502,-0.02639238,0.00675456,0.06442124,0.05687806,0.03984115,0.03302538,-0.00739817,0.07332638,0.05084616,0.01425276,-0.18790399,0.07941771,0.02165646,-0.00112141,-0.03282046,0.0024003,0.0135506,0.05043838,-0.11481265,-0.00473638,-0.02715886,0.03567119,0.11202954,0.00391823,0.01720386,-0.05068612,0.00159056,0.00016292,0.0261585,0.04785258,-0.01943243,-0.05156963,0.02431774,-0.04197187,0.00875094,-0.0095804,0.00224