"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[change] Updated Topic: Hive-Mind Model Discovery Engine (Hermes Standard): The user has confirmed and detailed the current project topic, \"Phase 7: Hive-Mind Model Discovery Engine (Hermes Standard)\". This phase focuses on porting Hermes's advanced model discovery logic to Hive-Mind. The plan involves creating a Python engine to intelligently identify available LLM models by analyzing configuration files and querying local services like Ollama and LM Studio. This engine will then be integrated into the Hive-Mind installation script, providing an interactive step for users to select their desired models from a comprehensive list of providers.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"196pchw","at":1782088664521},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.08060188,0.01131685,0.04442066,-0.10451107,0.0066285,0.0630241,-0.05307031,-0.01407303,0.02425462,-0.03103216,0.04749166,-0.07686614,0.00552628,0.0429162,0.03016503,0.01314202,0.02800542,-0.00321471,0.00285564,0.02429825,0.04312395,-0.03291962,0.01764366,-0.05483191,-0.02720679,0.03901478,0.00313416,0.00769332,-0.02276274,-0.23136291,0.02866714,-0.03299428,0.01789684,-0.00600507,-0.01815915,-0.00753067,0.00376904,0.02302131,-0.01108756,0.03050969,0.00738141,-0.01769793,-0.00503423,-0.00382169,-0.046875,-0.00784343,0.01426165,0.00534635,-0.05980736,-0.09237423,-0.04882341,-0.01520187,-0.04642629,-0.02744899,0.02461392,0.03825056,0.03831823,0.03614508,0.01474734,0.04666299,0.02970392,-0.0090981,-0.19048166,0.07127075,0.05781897,0.0128625,-0.03752922,-0.05371931,0.02617319,0.0155438,-0.04197418,0.00200258,0.01833877,0.03621236,0.06111303,0.03536504,-0.04218654,-0.03930223,0.02810702,-0.01283731,-0.04617454,0.00325413,-0.02600298,-0.04904674,-0.00725365,0.00405438,0.01706233,0.01141055,-0.00983473,-0.02592141,-0.02897872,-0.00019201,-0.03580093,0.01354164,0.00192108,0.03953344,0.02454159,-0.02051572,-0.02674114,0.1376859