n interactive step for users to select their desired models from a comprehensive list of providers.","lines":[23,24],"size":654,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[bugfix] Model Discovery Script Creation: A Python script named `model_discovery.py` has been created in the `scripts` directory. This script is designed to automate the process of discovering available LLM providers and their corresponding models. It intelligently checks for credentials and configurations in Hermes's `auth.json`, local `.env` files, and running local services like Ollama and LM Studio. The script then queries these providers to compile a list of discoverable models, outputting the results in JSON format for potential integration into the Hive-Mind setup process.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"19y3cwn","at":1782088664559},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.10406744,-0.00293215,0.07121606,-0.08285379,-0.03071037,0.00639861,-0.03615441,-0.01025842,0.02979928,-0.00535716,0.05861117,-0.05745487,0.02079139,0.0431818,0.00562369,-0.02552434,-0.02356756,-0.00494628,0.02551953,0.03463651,0.06736539,-0.00408868,-0.00862255,-0.0668207,-0.01128413,0.10444679,0.02887189,0.01705187,-0.02547588,-0.23474312,0.03731955,-0.0498254,0.01326522,-0.02759481,0.02744403,0.00690174,-0.0213489,0.00476212,-0.0088547,0.07236195,0.00727243,-0.04236198,0.00764292,-0.01689675,-0.02007838,-0.07537749,-0.02183889,-0.00898004,-0.02333439,-0.02916421,-0.03658803,-0.0292226,-0.04564666,-0.02840739,0.0228905,-0.00178503,0.03932124,0.06519455,0.00218342,0.04131056,0.01878678,0.0543753,-0.20702447,0.07538292,0.07315126,0.04355053,-0.01883486,-0.05169114,0.06105398,-0.02602273,-0.05827928,0.00504455,-0.01270635,0.04200719,0.02856408,-0.00272693,-0.0112121,-0.05285399,0.05188971,-0.03198828,-0.01118041,0.00709012,-0.02143016,-0.02474912,-0.0169329,-0.03796508,0.01944799,0.05752219,0.01803876,0.00517047,-0.0173912,0.00813066,-0.0608431,0.06715707,-0.05537071,0.02210763,0.05669061,-0.0148274,-0.02973876,0.1308866,-0.05105326,0.04385225,-0.03670371,-0.0390451,0.02590379,-0.027