"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[bugfix] Interactive Setup Script for Hive-Dreamer: An interactive shell script, `setup-dreamer.sh`, has been created to facilitate the configuration of the Hive-Dreamer component. This script leverages the previously generated `model_discovery.py` to dynamically list available LLM providers and their models. Users are presented with a menu to select their preferred provider and model, and the chosen configuration is then saved to the project's `.env` file. This script is a crucial step in integrating the model discovery logic into the Hive-Mind setup process.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1hehn9t","at":1782088664599},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07642248,0.02638908,0.04700962,-0.10850123,-0.04399118,0.07148848,-0.08057962,-0.04475153,0.01064781,0.00665402,0.04119008,-0.06425986,0.02605768,0.00326387,0.03507212,0.01085196,-0.01082195,0.02606318,0.02219523,0.0504379,0.03260263,0.0144499,0.00791468,-0.0366285,-0.00920339,0.07345042,-0.01945866,-0.00942202,-0.05475403,-0.20006925,0.05705574,-0.06381931,0.03145782,-0.00626818,-0.01734089,-0.01453449,0.01979113,0.03565335,-0.03232772,0.0680344,0.01353153,-0.04540944,0.00504971,-0.0086482,-0.01203417,-0.05796334,-0.02378501,-0.0562528,-0.02850273,-0.01914119,-0.06107254,-0.00257903,-0.00669513,0.00196458,0.00741665,0.0398576,0.01399887,0.06081909,0.06207627,0.04902431,0.01901102,0.06386391,-0.17166767,0.06252678,0.09446116,0.01896082,-0.04353629,-0.08217913,0.0789636,0.00032205,-0.06990405,0.02571073,0.0222807,0.03661984,0.04382906,-0.01500026,-0.02885566,-0.02447527,0.04262633,-0.03272245,-0.05072951,-0.00536215,-0.04386181,-0.03899372,-0.02391652,-0.02339999,0.00034559,0.01541013,-0.01296225,0.04904963,-0.03442632,-0.0016567,-0.05692609,0.0327127,-0.06540414,0.00702119,0.02944222,-0.03245396,-0.06648427,0.13894254,-0.02400126,0.02194974,-0.02338868,-0.06090743,0.01702815,-0.05505824,-0.01875786,-0