"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[security_alert] Blocked Command Injection Attempt: A security alert was triggered because an attempt was made to execute a shell command that utilized command substitution syntax (`$()` or backticks). This is flagged as a potential command injection vulnerability. The system successfully blocked the execution of this command to prevent security risks. The command was intended to create or modify the `scripts/setup-dreamer.sh` script, which is part of the Hive-Mind setup process.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1myeoko","at":1782088664637},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.02144347,0.00304431,0.03759488,-0.04682623,0.02387992,0.00739884,0.08098555,0.00547411,-0.00765808,0.03239724,0.01615345,-0.00957269,0.00968326,0.02149897,-0.01015044,0.03534786,-0.03010527,0.00708225,0.00901212,0.05495938,0.03649565,0.0678822,0.00777396,-0.03997786,-0.0140101,0.08005551,-0.02098095,-0.03431047,-0.05189694,-0.1625804,0.05713439,-0.06610586,-0.03633461,-0.05882062,-0.00815705,-0.01428348,-0.03375949,0.0481598,-0.03270553,0.0709044,0.02730733,-0.01762986,-0.00654659,-0.02345075,-0.02233262,-0.07279132,-0.05144566,-0.05279339,-0.00401372,0.00312893,-0.0243076,-0.00450592,0.03416698,-0.0096248,0.00786837,-0.05196469,-0.01148894,0.05072316,0.01907776,0.09059739,-0.01213644,0.0667595,-0.16113946,0.07103074,0.08456384,-0.00190158,-0.01571101,-0.02375007,0.05571017,0.06076185,-0.06044025,0.0111598,-0.02341857,0.06906468,0.00355615,-0.01057732,-0.00388843,-0.00838981,0.0318572,-0.05469466,-0.01132981,-0.06898978,0.02330351,-0.05937041,-0.0383298,-0.02854955,0.0343504,0.02718538,0.07981622,0.03001697,-0.01553974,0.006727,0.02093062,-0.02293655,-0.05622822,0.00259249,0.01760252,0.00062786,-0.11876862,0.12536411,-0.00069205,-0.01027054,-0.08738502,-0.01869387,0.0600513,-0.01588956,0.01054508,-0.05608075,-0.02929644,-0.03687602,-0.00581092,-0.03218312,0.11077973,-0.08000255,-0.