"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[bugfix] Updated Hive-Dreamer Setup Script: The `setup-dreamer.sh` script has been updated. This revision includes improvements to the user interaction, specifically using `printf` for prompts and `read` for capturing user input, which is a more robust way to handle interactive shell scripts. Additionally, the script now includes better error handling for cases where no LLM providers are detected and safely retrieves model lists, preventing potential errors if a provider has no models configured. The core functionality of saving the selected Hive-Dreamer provider and model to the `.env` file remains intact.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"i4t2ct","at":1782088664667},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06061871,0.00055752,0.03272439,-0.11111871,-0.02067707,0.05998679,-0.07919008,-0.00930628,-0.02343471,0.02737446,0.03632183,-0.07037921,0.02562593,0.01937498,0.01322803,0.01857362,0.00329112,0.00807037,0.01732902,0.05169548,-0.00188269,0.01775969,0.01808311,-0.02340447,-0.04257471,0.06688536,-0.03562341,-0.024723,-0.08305179,-0.2044528,0.04191445,-0.05697741,0.01262069,-0.00813357,-0.02328407,-0.02550041,0.00833954,0.00579532,0.00053418,0.0598439,0.00588334,-0.03308494,-0.01516818,-0.00923686,-0.02466471,-0.04233944,-0.02260057,-0.05221475,-0.01654891,-0.02375212,-0.07168628,0.01385681,0.01925778,-0.01310505,0.02348917,0.0099283,0.03091182,0.07934901,0.03588778,0.05062202,0.0156664,0.06986018,-0.17735745,0.08682637,0.09491828,0.01400794,-0.02863406,-0.0721246,0.03286997,0.01696853,-0.08863172,0.01655687,0.00230671,0.05990933,0.03104168,-0.03813298,0.0000022,-0.02334727,0.02012651,-0.03099372,-0.05078084,-0.00703822,-0.01377694,-0.05369389,-0.01440796,-0.01627855,0.02637882,0.02137418,-0.01013611,0.02767775,-0.02167503,0.00301722,-0.02005302,0.0593382,-0.06191502,0.01773505,0.04424992,-0.01258443,-0.08999036,0.12463978,-0.02048634,0.02269346,-0.02617362,-0