e `.env` file remains intact.","lines":[31,32],"size":618,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[bugfix] Execution of Hive-Dreamer Setup Script: The `setup-dreamer.sh` script was executed to simulate the interactive setup process for Hive-Dreamer. The script was first made executable, and then run with predefined inputs (`1` and `2`). These inputs are interpreted by the script to select an LLM provider and a specific model from the discovered list. This execution is a validation step to ensure that the model discovery and selection mechanism within the setup script functions as intended.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"15tlt9h","at":1782088664705},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.08303796,0.01343062,0.04700844,-0.11787556,-0.04175978,0.07158214,-0.06496546,-0.02442674,0.01294589,0.00067749,0.02325827,-0.03153826,0.03791037,0.01644632,0.03450108,0.01898745,-0.01555665,0.0330039,-0.00463331,0.04255796,0.04480094,0.01261793,0.00788292,-0.05372455,-0.00711806,0.05929163,-0.00836168,-0.01621976,-0.06627829,-0.19578221,0.05945278,-0.06602376,0.04014478,-0.01237615,-0.02912095,-0.01075314,-0.00285385,0.03015463,-0.04946253,0.05139542,0.02382025,-0.05497928,-0.00902619,-0.00769935,-0.01154784,-0.05683994,-0.02326115,-0.07213715,-0.03398978,0.00275401,-0.07897113,-0.00744394,0.01726756,-0.02839926,0.03357678,0.00165341,0.00913316,0.05887537,0.02621544,0.05012799,0.01432201,0.05571571,-0.16080888,0.07226077,0.09004649,0.0311257,-0.02038686,-0.08115217,0.0674294,0.02671619,-0.09670076,0.00320632,0.02206583,0.02867607,0.03185388,-0.0243806,-0.0298654,-0.01897657,0.02426289,-0.01758002,-0.03368033,-0.03536871,-0.01738366,-0.02882678,-0.02726972,0.00243001,0.00147738,0.02868525,-0.00516837,0.04650766,-0.00483447,-0.01445295,-0.05592008,0.03243333,-0.0385531,0.0049762,0.02809315,-0.02345869,-0.048889,0.13820435,-0.01498729,0.01249413,-0.03477418,-0.03184899,0.028501,-0.062362,-0.03429028,-0.03821608,-0.02085429,-0.03597765,-0.00197409,-0.02094977,0.06582621,