"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[bugfix] Successful Execution of Hive-Dreamer Setup Script: The `setup-dreamer.sh` script was executed successfully, demonstrating the automated discovery and selection of LLM providers and models. The script correctly identified available providers and presented them to the user. With the provided inputs, 'google' was selected as the provider and 'gemini-2.0-flash-exp' as the model. The script then confirmed the successful configuration and updated the `.env` file accordingly, indicating that Hive-Dreamer is now set up with the chosen LLM.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1jce55q","at":1782088664768},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07429512,-0.00269838,0.06305762,-0.1072573,-0.02745412,0.06896151,-0.08581976,-0.01141689,-0.00114054,-0.00374488,0.02918513,-0.02193154,0.02848711,0.02016564,0.01903357,0.02605198,-0.00582999,-0.01218118,0.00228246,0.06446028,0.04231711,0.00143151,0.03634408,-0.01539409,-0.00255056,0.04802452,-0.034196,-0.03772739,-0.07475876,-0.19811194,0.04129381,-0.08062424,0.02150782,-0.02273227,-0.02355152,-0.01277756,0.01060617,0.02269008,-0.03834285,0.04221185,0.01024466,-0.07063477,-0.0238772,-0.01616686,-0.0202075,-0.0516761,-0.02346934,-0.0431596,-0.04083122,-0.020914,-0.04402488,0.00277481,0.01271543,-0.00308558,-0.00257704,0.00969895,-0.00339033,0.04951899,0.03024733,0.0582208,0.01740548,0.04193684,-0.1884464,0.05968935,0.06344563,0.0470272,-0.02867683,-0.08679797,0.05788852,0.02823545,-0.08745677,0.02934234,0.01232455,0.02408403,0.02475858,0.01075784,-0.00785835,-0.01980144,0.00883357,-0.03150368,-0.04350155,-0.0221615,-0.04136638,-0.0473502,-0.00634067,0.00775343,0.01348376,0.02289108,-0.01308383,0.04051909,-0.00380017,0.00284202,-0.04857581,0.04017945,-0.04327067,0.01767596,0.03610131,-0.02016818,-0.06827309,0.13098855,-0.02111332,0.02790713,-0.02722488,-0.03333799,0.02243249,-0.07384148,-0.02175248,-0.03006842,-0.0219769