"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[feature] Integrated LLM Provider Configuration: The user expressed frustration with previous attempts and emphasized the need for a unified installation script that handles the configuration of multiple LLM providers. This new approach centralizes the setup process, allowing for dynamic selection and integration of models like Codex, Claude, Gemini, and Ollama (both cloud and local instances), as well as LM Studio. Authentication for these providers will be managed through API keys and OAuth protocols, ensuring a robust and flexible system.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"kfoxtw","at":1782088664804},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09890608,-0.02968748,0.04901147,-0.07619304,-0.02328451,0.01595543,-0.04836326,-0.02171486,0.02769032,-0.05397945,0.0129879,-0.00611228,0.05136806,0.01625536,0.03504065,0.01265503,-0.01260798,0.00735354,0.00767116,0.06073756,0.09173257,-0.01726427,0.02520186,0.00497073,-0.02554805,0.02726332,-0.04446694,-0.03523158,-0.03521917,-0.21982904,0.03696614,0.00152989,0.03551743,-0.04402728,-0.02912094,-0.02723726,-0.06504969,0.02496811,-0.01765758,0.05594027,0.01444647,-0.04125869,-0.03383074,-0.04189413,-0.01390186,-0.09512494,-0.02956134,-0.01035725,-0.04004611,-0.00572459,0.05851453,-0.01805452,-0.00070516,0.01383604,-0.01257693,0.0198742,-0.01867001,0.03968791,0.00733486,0.08996589,0.03635948,0.04221606,-0.20067881,0.08570165,0.02207479,0.05719921,-0.02286849,0.0156929,0.06396736,0.06710365,-0.06933931,-0.04327204,0.01950757,-0.00806953,0.04960991,0.02219752,0.0082932,0.01239246,0.01463616,-0.03966695,0.01228744,0.03686542,-0.01558249,-0.08096599,-0.03841332,-0.00523702,-0.01910139,-0.00837196,-0.03764285,0.03470936,-0.04343368,0.01088396,-0.03897025,0.02388611,-0.02576458,-0.00944741,0.02214884,-0.04330821,-0.07356356,0.12589772,-0.03271256,-0.00345765,0.00907176,-0.03093182,0.01790925,-0.0326681,-0.02428891,-0.01054699,-0