"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[feature] Integrated LLM Provider Configuration: The user expressed frustration with the previous installation script's limited LLM provider integration. The updated script now centralizes the configuration for a wide array of LLM providers, including commercial APIs (Codex, Claude, Gemini) and local/self-hosted options (Ollama, LM Studio). This allows for flexible and robust LLM integration within the tool, leveraging their respective authentication mechanisms (API keys and OAuth).": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"a9kha4","at":1782088664837},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.10041786,-0.03352023,0.06422087,-0.06309623,-0.02016198,-0.02194364,-0.04143791,-0.00501614,0.03054687,-0.07238381,0.01896534,0.00435346,0.06170096,0.01799838,0.02755762,0.01882499,-0.01391513,0.00253071,-0.00665469,0.05866637,0.09361813,-0.01442282,0.02115874,0.01951536,-0.02877078,0.02933107,-0.04788612,-0.017636,-0.05261029,-0.21862015,0.05059453,-0.01611322,0.03372706,-0.05954866,-0.03080222,-0.01554823,-0.08632036,0.02680482,0.0029785,0.06228631,0.02582735,-0.0370127,-0.04565483,-0.04094419,-0.04001542,-0.09456456,-0.01393145,-0.01760821,-0.02975284,-0.00158227,0.04953049,-0.02296566,0.00531643,0.0259814,-0.00930903,0.0329493,-0.00936098,0.03781359,0.02994693,0.09592178,0.0490459,0.03452829,-0.21778278,0.09790564,0.0016062,0.0430352,-0.01709888,0.01559223,0.0616683,0.05680762,-0.06255627,-0.04192064,0.02458124,-0.00908151,0.05364515,0.0312354,0.01420781,-0.00080332,0.02094291,-0.03361711,0.00172864,0.02890125,-0.01059138,-0.10835999,-0.02544549,-0.01909452,-0.0177741,-0.02962383,-0.01191261,0.03216992,-0.03169661,-0.01414109,-0.05927604,0.0242621,-0.02390451,0.00009585,0.03849069,-0.04034486,-0.06595611,0.13110012,-0.04580563,0.00537449,-0.01041265,-0.02850395,0.01742114,-0.03091659,-0.02827692,0.00267164,-0.02333509,0.01395766,-0.03310121,0.01977935,0.06552023,-0.06010269,-