"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[feature] Integrate Multiple LLM Providers via API Keys and OAuth: The user expressed frustration with the previous approach and emphasized the need for a unified installation script that handles the configuration of various LLM providers. This update ensures the tool can dynamically identify and utilize available models through their respective APIs, supporting authentication via API keys and OAuth. The script is designed to be comprehensive, allowing for parallel configurations and the integration of providers beyond the initial focus, such as Codex, Claude, Gemini, and Ollama (both cloud and local instances), as well as LM Studio.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"9o898l","at":1782088664867},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.10597873,-0.04859638,0.03082418,-0.08272494,-0.05663097,-0.00382512,-0.04210264,-0.03045332,0.02665264,-0.06392507,0.00082487,-0.00670704,0.04974447,-0.00820917,0.01638648,-0.01901313,-0.01800099,0.00681349,-0.00190175,0.04303604,0.08302886,-0.00121247,0.02755666,0.00198956,-0.04769163,0.04868745,-0.06323084,-0.02991439,-0.04102104,-0.21803012,0.03111604,-0.00536533,0.04268514,-0.03019774,-0.0370478,-0.01767316,-0.05508472,0.03306705,-0.00863564,0.05647109,0.02156779,-0.04188467,-0.03284821,-0.0765426,-0.01300651,-0.07648029,-0.05369218,0.01759062,-0.04304377,-0.00504419,0.05533924,0.01141266,0.00572924,0.02577324,0.01871191,0.00932084,-0.01488748,0.06442973,0.01994807,0.10257682,0.05099244,0.03904966,-0.18656288,0.10734615,0.01164581,0.06618171,-0.00615906,-0.00517468,0.05829439,0.04836255,-0.04588522,-0.04148848,0.01460574,-0.0140706,0.04573464,0.02590181,-0.01790071,0.00185738,0.00988242,-0.05525218,-0.02211641,0.02839217,-0.00707713,-0.06607133,-0.04502673,-0.02503295,-0.01588792,-0.01042114,-0.01537325,0.01996107,-0.04011729,-0.0151337,-0.02639998,0.02400726,-0.01164249,0.01779203,0.04141717,-0.02749845,-0.09205057,0.137011