e, Gemini, and Ollama (both cloud and local instances), as well as LM Studio.","lines":[43,44],"size":645,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[decision] Project Phase 7 Rework - Authentication and Model Selection: The user has directed a significant rework of Phase 7 for the Hive-Mind project. The core requirement is to implement a robust authentication system that supports both OAuth and API key methods. This system should be designed to mirror the authentication flows observed in the Hermes project, specifically how it handles OAuth and API key logins. Crucially, the Hive-Mind implementation should not directly use Hermes but rather learn from its patterns. Following successful authentication, the system must then present the user with a selection of available models. Before any code is written, a thorough study of the authentication mechanisms and a detailed implementation plan are mandated.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1j9v1m","at":1782088664905},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.0748839,-0.00018296,-0.03834373,-0.12143552,-0.04083868,0.072005,-0.02813467,0.00183836,0.01255198,-0.00904201,0.02761771,-0.04925523,-0.00951554,0.0304995,0.01743138,0.01010429,0.02800076,0.0282732,0.02220255,0.04821451,0.02262066,-0.02581943,0.03058154,-0.04939911,-0.03441015,0.02078078,-0.03597508,0.00059741,-0.02043063,-0.21277425,0.00453606,-0.02752591,0.00446574,-0.00583662,-0.02272421,-0.02570679,0.00001627,0.00569174,-0.03189234,0.02134666,0.00155323,0.01108365,-0.01257419,-0.02552176,-0.01966701,-0.00209007,-0.01662416,0.02556006,-0.05807193,-0.07581597,0.0000127,0.00756156,-0.00933157,0.01336327,0.02247278,0.03227716,0.03329201,0.07194531,-0.01889969,0.06193328,0.04851538,0.00180524,-0.18117052,0.0723452,0.0658834,0.04722231,-0.04368174,-0.04578589,0.02553755,0.04401639,-0.0735151,0.0069705,-0.01336059,0.02846087,0.05084518,0.02843093,-0.06017266,-0.0298563,0.04546377,-0.03618817,-0.04843864,0.01016599,-0.00585877,-0.00277403,-0.02422844,0.02512513,0.00294278,-0.02822977,-0.01475634,-0.04397755,-0