"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[discovery] Consolidated Note Naming Conflict: The user is inquiring about how the system handles consolidated notes that share the same name. They are concerned that this could lead to the creation of document silos, where information is fragmented, or that all notes with the same name might be written into a single file, which they deem undesirable. This highlights a potential design flaw or an area needing clarification regarding unique identifier management for consolidated notes.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"v5u8e6","at":1782088664950},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05471433,-0.02328395,0.04563324,-0.04994465,-0.02148377,-0.01479046,0.00055226,0.0076735,0.05353512,0.01516378,0.00491758,0.02302138,0.03332382,0.0060576,0.00405108,-0.01123296,-0.03104479,-0.02387192,0.03098723,0.04040625,0.08767728,0.00404759,0.01176003,0.04665325,-0.02721132,0.07781025,-0.02472831,-0.04749203,-0.08031664,-0.2452125,-0.0001665,0.02712521,0.06344382,-0.02384728,0.0196041,-0.01006339,-0.01967906,0.10010596,-0.04506365,0.08853941,0.00285392,0.02808692,0.01726711,0.01606733,-0.02231579,-0.03702971,-0.04116482,-0.04641167,0.03872484,0.00911165,-0.03793598,-0.04640402,-0.03732368,0.0023269,-0.04291818,0.03689053,0.03185757,-0.00042002,0.02538339,0.08082481,0.05857747,0.005432,-0.20934595,0.08459826,0.05467221,0.00922261,-0.02049475,0.01021452,-0.01379957,0.07082554,-0.05292693,0.02804531,-0.01255056,0.07901862,0.01755085,-0.0402748,0.00964727,-0.01457431,-0.03549472,-0.03853811,-0.04788619,0.0100212,-0.00002981,-0.05191349,-0.06549233,0.00281828,0.01615636,-0.0327259,0.00460484,-0.01815843,-0.0010208,-0.04404196,0.06755524,0.03149304,-0.08397631,-0.05258512,0.0091885,0.0250007,-0.06515379,0.12397682,-0.02671494,0.03594247,0.06898812,-0.02040422,0.02930008,0.00054045,0.0387749,-0.04980929,-0.03234828,-0.02200407,-0.00195465,-0.01567821,-0.01030866,-0.06373894,0.0058