"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[change] LLM Council Skill Activated: The 'llm-council' skill has been activated. This skill is designed to provide a more robust answer to complex questions by running them through five distinct \"advisors\" (Contrarian, First Principles Thinker, Expansionist, Outsider, Executor) who analyze the question from different angles. Their responses are then peer-reviewed, and a chairman synthesizes the findings into a final verdict and recommendation. The skill emphasizes its use for questions where being wrong is costly and provides detailed steps for framing the question, convening the council, conducting peer review, and synthesizing the results.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1665du6","at":1782088665098},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09546356,0.01017727,0.04266355,-0.01457954,-0.03753132,0.03044095,0.03795121,0.00644757,-0.01284572,-0.05021921,0.04777269,-0.00545199,0.01208845,0.03148498,0.01495257,0.02777719,-0.01485192,0.02532417,0.04002635,0.03759158,0.03973484,-0.02901862,0.0302084,0.02011809,-0.00071548,-0.02775649,-0.04608029,-0.08566619,-0.10511569,-0.22793017,0.04884223,-0.01864119,0.05903834,-0.02474356,-0.06821647,-0.04625656,-0.0773154,0.0217835,-0.04657858,0.06240089,0.01066471,-0.03726602,0.00039516,-0.02371819,-0.01199177,-0.04943258,-0.01730529,-0.07298563,-0.03126544,-0.00090753,-0.09370411,-0.07509697,0.01422914,-0.02505993,0.04883081,0.0156955,0.0022614,0.03869068,0.03574185,0.09521931,0.06856709,0.05171432,-0.24105005,0.11717111,-0.0027877,0.04078469,-0.05220898,0.0168638,0.04254228,0.06201008,-0.01414625,-0.02184574,0.05259601,0.00010974,0.0427957,0.0089638,-0.05015707,0.00351128,0.0295075,-0.04396046,-0.00878622,0.03256197,-0.00070297,-0.09504174,-0.01018811,-0.03494697,-0.02245197,0.03793669,0.01621321,0.02471607,0.05372614,0.01618522,-0.04607467,0.04792712,-0.04183451,-0.04348153,0.01885682,0.0057856,-0.12359884,0.1439748,-