"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[change] Brainstorming Skill Activated: The 'brainstorming' skill has been activated. This skill guides a collaborative process to refine ideas into detailed designs and specifications. It mandates a strict workflow, starting with exploring project context, asking clarifying questions one at a time, proposing approaches, presenting a design for approval, writing a design document, self-reviewing the spec, and finally getting user approval before invoking the 'writing-plans' skill for implementation. The skill also includes instructions for handling visual companion tools and emphasizes principles like YAGNI and incremental validation.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"od1m2v","at":1782088665139},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04915999,0.01912935,0.02370979,-0.0546105,-0.06638283,0.0932118,0.00083046,0.05896398,-0.03205057,-0.00454556,0.01680093,-0.01229356,0.00236211,0.03293534,-0.01110298,0.0271956,-0.04220907,0.02825876,0.04657138,-0.01263374,0.03839557,-0.00228648,0.0206163,-0.00163963,0.01202077,0.03962801,-0.04523278,-0.10819626,-0.0798865,-0.20352195,0.0188434,-0.00046208,0.06421249,-0.04523601,-0.06818258,0.02114362,-0.08817974,0.05264879,0.00758388,-0.01524783,0.01847897,0.01584453,-0.03779902,-0.03897773,-0.01318136,-0.03998902,-0.05966274,-0.08199847,0.00071451,-0.02246106,-0.1052307,-0.07672226,-0.01885282,-0.01042629,0.02773869,0.05310397,0.01565086,-0.01565049,0.03360495,0.09884764,0.04040187,0.04100318,-0.18328641,0.14452256,0.01835213,0.02288779,-0.05647023,0.00294788,0.00996785,0.05193144,-0.02656697,-0.01659902,0.0704031,0.06604854,0.06065181,0.01810856,-0.0524074,-0.0244734,0.02779047,-0.05473682,-0.0331151,0.03630272,0.03229293,-0.02414069,0.00199413,0.01139832,0.0197867,0.00187612,-0.01047663,0.00917218,0.02391504,0.00033274,-0.0512449,0.02948093,-0.08776716,-0.02144128,0.02961658,-0.0379085,-0.12018066,0.13936077,-0.05261858,-0.