"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1005-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:05#[refactor] Revisiting Hive-Mind Phase 7 Authentication and API Key Integration: The user has requested a re-evaluation of Phase 7 for the Hive-Mind project. The core task is to study how the 'Hermes' system handles OAuth and API key authentication. The goal is to implement a similar authentication flow within Hive-Mind, but without directly using Hermes. After successful authentication (via OAuth or API key), the system should then display available models for selection. This requires a thorough understanding of Hermes' existing implementation before proceeding with the Hive-Mind development plan.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"ba8r26","at":1782088665173},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06813313,-0.00231496,-0.01841863,-0.10253607,-0.05174407,0.06709408,-0.01209581,-0.00866053,0.01621449,-0.02459224,0.04059324,-0.07346228,0.01748098,0.01761634,0.01425327,-0.00121379,0.02524103,0.01778429,-0.01410366,0.03358714,0.00263003,-0.02333203,0.03151263,-0.04093305,-0.06234548,0.03716006,-0.03410275,-0.00210881,-0.03693812,-0.19515535,0.03642262,-0.0396406,0.01208327,-0.00302289,-0.04522503,-0.0209435,0.01087765,0.01540584,-0.04714477,0.01140656,0.03809553,0.01303084,-0.01837905,-0.01907661,-0.02982833,-0.02266609,-0.02394487,0.03337663,-0.04891462,-0.05875861,-0.01673508,0.0225625,-0.00335967,0.02485049,0.02929343,0.05154417,0.01412748,0.06370693,0.01761536,0.06335711,0.05873578,-0.01943207,-0.16557822,0.08089975,0.06758527,0.04804935,-0.04350479,-0.06352106,0.01385708,0.03401411,-0.06985265,0.0180969,-0.00283354,0.04132122,0.05282882,0.02929839,-0.07170408,-0.02407203,0.03328814,-0.03770547,-0.06327632,0.020871,-0.00088493,0.00700315,-0.02567933,0.03109461,-0.00563238,-0.02824234,-0.0092535,-0.02498636,-0.02029071,-0.04179372,-0.03990064,-0.01261077,0.01852761,0.0328677,0.03221655,0.00979542,-0.0561174,0.1226071,-0.01714396,0.01250767,-0.03535125,-0.09906